         <div xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268"><!-- p2l6-r6 -->
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-Hd1e108">Rubrica 6</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De iure et lege et pacto</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-d1e114">
               <lb ed="#V" n="1"/>
      ¶ De iure lege et pacto. Rubrica. 6.
    </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-d1e119">
               <lb ed="#V" n="2"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-Rd1e115">ISaias propheta. c. 10.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-Qd1e123">Uhe qua
        <lb ed="#V" n="3"/>condunt leges iniquas</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-d1e129">
               <lb ed="#V" n="4"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-Rd1e127">Cronica de nugisphilosophurum. c. 3 scilicet de
        <lb ed="#V" n="5"/>solone:</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-Qd1e133">Solon qui fuit vnus de 
               se<lb ed="#V" n="6" break="no"/>ptem sapiententibus dicebat leges fuliginibus
        <lb ed="#V" n="7"/>similes: etenim in illas siquid inciderit quod
        <lb ed="#V" n="8"/>leue et debile sustinere. Si vero maius 
               residen<lb ed="#V" n="9" break="no"/>tes ire.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-d1e148"> /
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-Rd1e147">2. c. scilicet de chilone.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-Qd1e150">Chilo 
               lacedemo<lb ed="#V" n="10" break="no"/>nius qui fuit vnus de. vii. sapiententibus 
               iu<lb ed="#V" n="11" break="no"/>bebat legibus obedire.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-d1e158">
               <lb ed="#V" n="12"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-Rd1e161">Isocrates in exhortationibus. c. 2.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-Qd1e162">
               Obtem<lb ed="#V" n="13" break="no"/>pera legibus. Obedias legibus que regibus
        <lb ed="#V" n="14"/>subsunt.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-d1e170">
               <lb ed="#V" n="15"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-Rd1e175">Aristoteles retho. li. i. c. 10.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-Qd1e174">Iudicium quidem
        <lb ed="#V" n="16"/>legistatoris non secundum partem sed de futuris
        <lb ed="#V" n="17"/>et vniuersalibus est.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-d1e182"> /
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-Rd1e187">6. c.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-Qd1e184">In legibus est 
               sa<lb ed="#V" n="18" break="no"/>lus ciuitatis.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-d1e190"> /
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-Rd1e197">18. c.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-Qd1e192">Praua facere preter 
               le<lb ed="#V" n="19" break="no"/>gem malitia est et incontinentia.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-d1e198"> /
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-Rd1e207">45. c. et fi.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="20"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-Qd1e200">Pactum est lex propria et secundum partem.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-d1e207"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-Qd1e209">Lex 
               pa<lb ed="#V" n="21" break="no"/>ctum quoddam est. Pactum leges destruit.</quote> <!--quote with no ref-->
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-d1e215">
               <lb ed="#V" n="22"/>/
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-Rd1e229">Idem polliticorum libro i. c. 4.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-Qd1e219">Lex iustum 
               quod<lb ed="#V" n="23" break="no"/>dam est.
      </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-d1e225"> /
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-Rd1e239">Libro. 3 c. 9. et pe.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-Qd1e227">Sine appetitu
        <lb ed="#V" n="24"/>intellectus lex est.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-d1e233"> /
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-Rd1e249">Lib. 7. c. 3.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-Qd1e235">Lex ordo
        <lb ed="#V" n="25"/>quidam est.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-d1e241"> /
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-Rd1e259">Idem elacorum libro i.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-Qd1e243">Lex est 
               opi<lb ed="#V" n="26" break="no"/>nio plurium.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-d1e249">
               <lb ed="#V" n="27"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-Rd1e271">Tullius rethoricorum artis vereris li. 2. c. 5.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="28"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-Qd1e253">Initium inuris a natura ductum videtur. 
               Natu<lb ed="#V" n="29" break="no"/>re quidem ius est quod nobis non opinio: sed quae
        <lb ed="#V" n="30"/>dam innata vis afferat: vt religionem: 
               pieta<lb ed="#V" n="31" break="no"/>tem: gratiam: vindicationem: obseruantiam: 
               ve<lb ed="#V" n="32" break="no"/>ritatem. Consuetudinis ius esse putatur id
        <lb ed="#V" n="33"/>quod voluntate omnium sine lege vetustas 
               con<lb ed="#V" n="34" break="no"/>probaret. Pactum est quod inter quos conuenit
        <lb ed="#V" n="35"/><unclear>ita</unclear> iustum putatur vt iuri prestare dicatur.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-d1e275"> /
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-Rd1e297">c.
        <lb ed="#V" n="36"/>9</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-Qd1e277">Consuetudine ius est quod aut leuiter a 
               na<lb ed="#V" n="37" break="no"/>tura tractum aluit: et in maius facit vsus: vt 
               re<lb ed="#V" n="38" break="no"/>ligionem: aut siquid eorum que ante diximus a
        <lb ed="#V" n="39"/>natura profectum: maius factum propter 
               consue<lb ed="#V" n="40" break="no"/>tudinem videmus: aut quod in morem vetustas
        <lb ed="#V" n="41"/>vulgi approbatione perduxit. Pactum est quod
        <lb ed="#V" n="42"/>inter aliquos conuenit. Lege ius est quod in eo
        <lb ed="#V" n="43"/>scripto quod populo exposito est vt obseruet
        <lb ed="#V" n="44"/>continetur.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-d1e300"> /
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-Rd1e325">Idem retho. artis noue libro
        <lb ed="#V" n="45"/>2. c. 4.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-Qd1e302">Lege huius est id quod iussu popu <!--138.xml-->
        <cb ed="#V" n="b"/>
                  <lb ed="#V" n="46"/>
        <lb ed="#V" n="47" break="no"/>li sancitum est. Consuetudinis ius est id
        <lb ed="#V" n="48"/>quod sine lege equo ac si legittimum sit 
               vsi<lb ed="#V" n="49" break="no"/>tatum est.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-d1e321"> /
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-Rd1e349">Idem de legibus libro. i.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-Qd1e323">Lex
        <lb ed="#V" n="50"/>est ratio summa in natura que iubet ea que
        <lb ed="#V" n="51"/>facienda sunt: proh ibet que contraria. 
               Le<lb ed="#V" n="52" break="no"/>gem bonam amala nulla alia nisi nature norma
        <lb ed="#V" n="53"/>diuidere possumus. Non sulum ius et iura
        <lb ed="#V" n="54"/>natura diuiduntur: sed omnino omnia 
               ho<lb ed="#V" n="55" break="no"/>nesta et turpia.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-d1e340"> /
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-Rd1e370">Idem de officiis libro. i. c.
        <lb ed="#V" n="56"/>39.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-Qd1e342">Qui parti ciuium consulunt: partem 
               negli<lb ed="#V" n="57" break="no"/>gunt rem pernitiosissimam in ciuitate inducunt
        <lb ed="#V" n="58"/>seditionem atque discordiam.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-d1e352"> /
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-Rd1e385">Idem 
               tu<lb ed="#V" n="59" break="no"/>sculanarum questionum li. i.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-Qd1e354">Consensio omnium
        <lb ed="#V" n="60"/>gentium lex nature putanda est.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-d1e362"> /
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-Rd1e398">Idem de
        <lb ed="#V" n="61"/>natura deorum libro. 2.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-Qd1e364">Lex est recti 
               prece<lb ed="#V" n="62" break="no"/>ptio: prauique depulsio.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-d1e373"> /
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-Rd1e412">Idem topicorum. c.
        <lb ed="#V" n="63"/>3.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-Qd1e375">Ius ciuile est equitas constituta: his qui
        <lb ed="#V" n="64"/>eiusdem sunt ciuitatis ad res suas obtinendas</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-d1e383">
               <lb ed="#V" n="65"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-Rd1e427">Seneca epistolarum ad lucillum lib. 16.
        <lb ed="#V" n="66"/>epistola. 2.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-Qd1e387">Legem breuem oportet esse quo
        <lb ed="#V" n="67"/>facilius ab imperitis teneatur: velut emissa
        <lb ed="#V" n="68"/>diuinitus vox sit: iubeat non disputet.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-d1e397">
               <lb ed="#V" n="69"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-Rd1e444">Ualerius maximus libro. 7 tit. sapienter
        <lb ed="#V" n="70"/>dicta aut facta:</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-Qd1e401">Anatharsis leges aranearum
        <lb ed="#V" n="71"/>telis comparabat: nam vt illas infirmiora
        <lb ed="#V" n="72"/>animalia retinere valentiora transmittem: ita his
        <lb ed="#V" n="73"/>humiles et pauperes constringi: diuites et 
               pre<lb ed="#V" n="74" break="no"/>potentes non alligari.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-d1e415">
               <lb ed="#V" n="75"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-Rd1e465">Lex diges. ti. de iustitia et iure libro. i.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-Qd1e419">Ius
        <lb ed="#V" n="76"/>est ars boni et equi.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-d1e425"> /
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-Rd1e475">l. iustitia</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-Qd1e427">Iuris 
               prece<lb ed="#V" n="77" break="no"/>precepta sunt hec: Honeste viuere: 
               alte<lb ed="#V" n="78" break="no"/>rum non ledere: suum cuique tribuere: 
      </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-d1e435"> /
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-Rd1e487">Ti.
      <lb ed="#V" n="79"/>de iniuriis. l. iniuriarum. §. i.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-Qd1e439">Iuris executio
        <lb ed="#V" n="80"/>non habet iniuriam.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-d1e446"> /
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-Rd1e501">Tit. ad leg. iulis de vi
        <lb ed="#V" n="81"/>pub. l. pe.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-Qd1e448">Non puto nec <sic>vcrecundie</sic> nec di <!--'c' isntead of 'e' for verecundie-->
        <lb ed="#V" n="82" break="no"/>gnitati: nec pietati conuenire: quicquam non iu
        <lb ed="#V" n="83"/>re facere.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-d1e458"> /
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-Rd1e520">Ti. de var. et extraor. cog. l. i. §. 
               pro<lb ed="#V" n="84" break="no"/>inde.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-Qd1e460">Est quidem res sanctissima ciuilis 
               sa<lb ed="#V" n="85" break="no"/>pientia: que praecio nummario non est estimanda.
        <lb ed="#V" n="86"/>Lex auten. ti. haec constitutio innouat etc. in prin <!--add ref?-->
        <lb ed="#V" n="87" break="no"/>cipio: Quod medicamenta morbis hoc exhi
        <lb ed="#V" n="88"/>bent iura negociis.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-d1e474">
               <lb ed="#V" n="89"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-Rd1e543">Macrobius saturnaliorum lib. 2. c. 20.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-Qd1e478">Nisi
        <lb ed="#V" n="90"/>pessimis effusisque moribus viueretur: profecto 
               fe<lb ed="#V" n="91" break="no"/>rendis lagibus opus non fuisset. <!--139.xml-->
      </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-d1e488">
               <pb ed="#V" n="56-v"/>
               <cb ed="#V" n="a"/>
               <lb ed="#V" n="1"/> /
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-Qd1e496">Leges bone ex malis moribus procreantur.</quote> <!--quote with no ref-->
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-d1e500">
               <lb ed="#V" n="2"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-Rd1e573">Cato. c. i.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-Qd1e504">Patere legem quam tuipse tuleris.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-d1e508">
               <lb ed="#V" n="3"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-Rd1e583">Cassiodorus epistolarum lib. 3. e. 17.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-Qd1e512">Iura
        <lb ed="#V" n="4"/>publi. certissime sunt humane vite solatia: 
               in<lb ed="#V" n="5" break="no"/>firmorum auxilia potentum frena.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-d1e521"> /
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-Rd1e596">Libro. 4.
        <lb ed="#V" n="6"/>e. 27.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-Qd1e523">Quicquid contra leges admittitur iusta 
               exe<lb ed="#V" n="7" break="no"/>cratione damnatur.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-d1e531"> /
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-Rd1e609">Lib. 5. e. 39.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-Qd1e533">Illa vere 
               vi<lb ed="#V" n="8" break="no"/>ta hominum est que inuris ordine continetur: nam
        <lb ed="#V" n="9"/>beluarum ritus est sub casu viuere que dum 
               ra<lb ed="#V" n="10" break="no"/>piendi ambitu feruntur improuisa temeritate
        <lb ed="#V" n="11"/>succumbunt.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-d1e545"> /
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-Rd1e625">Li. 9. e. 15.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-Qd1e547">Iustissime siquidem
        <lb ed="#V" n="12"/>leges vt bonis aperiunt: ita claudunt malis 
               mo<lb ed="#V" n="13" break="no"/>ribus actionem.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-d1e555">
               <lb ed="#V" n="14"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-Rd1e639">Montenarius in luna cleri. ca. 117.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42268-Qd1e559">Quando
        <lb ed="#V" n="15"/>iura silent: nequeunt peccata filere.</quote>
            </p>
